ca.corefacility.gview.style.datastyle

Class FeatureHolderStyle

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.corefacility.gview.style.datastyle.SlotItemStyle
      • ca.corefacility.gview.style.datastyle.FeatureHolderStyle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FeatureContainerStyle, PropertyMappable, StyleHolder

    public class FeatureHolderStyle
extends SlotItemStyle
implements StyleHolder, FeatureContainerStyle
    Stores the style information for a particular set of features. The set of features this applies to is filtered out by the passed filter.
    Author:
    Aaron Petkau
